<div class="WordSection1"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Honeywell Aerospace Singapore Pte.Ltd.</span><br /><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">2 Loyang Crescent</span><br /><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">508976 Singapore </span></div>
<p><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">July 27, 2015<br /><br /></span></p>
<p style="line-height: 115%;"><span style="line-height: 115%; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Dear Honeywell Customer,</span></p>
<p style="line-height: 115%;"><span style="line-height: 115%; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Last month we shared with you our SAP transition plans for the Singapore Loyang Avionic R&amp;O site. And we promised to provide you updates along the way. We are excited to say that we are still progressing towards a Sept. 27<sup>th</sup>, 2015, transition date.</span></p>
<p style="line-height: 115%;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="line-height: 115%;">You<span style="color: black;"> may recall, the Singapore SAP transition will result in a change to the Honeywell legal entity. Although the Singapore Loyang Avionic repairs will be performed at the same site, you will need to update the supplier information in your internal systems. <br /> <br /> </span></span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black;">To </span><span style="line-height: 115%;">minimize order disruptions</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black;">, here are the steps you&rsquo;ll want and need to take as a result of this change: <br /></span></span></p>
<ul>
<li><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Update your internal purchasing, authorized supplier list and quality management system (QMS) to reflect this legal entity name change. A <a href="https://pages3.honeywell.com/rs/641-QIX-912/images/Singapore 60 Day Transition Preparation Checklist .pdf" target="_blank">transition checklist</a><span style="color: red;"></span> is available and includes the new supplier address, amended &ldquo;Ship To&rdquo; address, and invoicing and payment bank details. <br /> </span></li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><strong>For Contract Customers only:</strong> Execute an Amendment Agreement to assign Contracts, to include HIS and/or delete HASPL/ HAPL from Contract, to amend Bank details, delivery /export clauses, notices address etc., where required. <u>Our Customer Business Managers and Contracts team have been in contact with your company to provide additional information to complete this action this month. </u></span></li>
</ul>
<span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="color: black;">If you have any questions or concerns, please reach out to your Honeywell Customer Business Manager or email us at </span><a href="mailto:AeroCPSCommunications@Honeywell.com"><span style="color: blue;">AeroCPSCommunications@Honeywell.com</span></a><span style="color: black;">. </span></span>
<p style="line-height: normal;"><span style="color: black; font-size: 16px; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><a href="https://pages3.honeywell.com/rs/641-QIX-912/images/CGM - 60 day letter - Chinese.pdf" target="_blank">Chinese translated letter</a><br /><a href="https://pages3.honeywell.com/rs/641-QIX-912/images/Singapore 60 Day Transition Preparation Checklist - Chinese .pdf" target="_blank">Chinese translated transition checklist</a><br /><br />Yours sincerely,</span></p>
<p style="line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><strong>Heath Patrick</strong></span><br /><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Vice President</span><br /><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Customer &amp; Product Support</span><br /><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Honeywell Aerospace <br /><br /><br /></span></p></div>
